name: 布伦丹·罗萨里
name_full: 布伦丹·罗萨里 Brendan Rozario

last_movies.title: 最后生还者 第二季

introduction: Brendan Rozario's love of film began as early as his first steps toward the television.At a young age he began to go regularly to theatre performances, his first being "Oliver!" which inspired him to take both stage and theatrical acting at the Shadbolt Center For The Arts.Brendan's passion continued while taking drama/film through high-school and continued to work on set while studying post secondary.
